  "title": "💼 (Fresh Grads! Travelling Opportunities!) Marketing Associate | Fun, Growth & Great Team Culture! 🌱",
  "description": "<p><strong>🚀 Join Our Marketing Crew! 🌟</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Full-Time | Training Provided | Entry Level | No Experience Needed</strong></p>\n<p>We’re a fast-growing team representing top brands in telco, NGOs &amp; lifestyle sectors! 🌏</p>\n<p>If you’re energetic, people-loving &amp; eager to grow — this is your stage! 💪</p>\n<p><strong>💼 What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>🎯 Represent clients at events &amp; roadshows</li>\n  <li>💬 Engage customers &amp; build awareness</li>\n  <li>🤝 Work with a fun, supportive team</li>\n  <li>📚 Learn sales, leadership &amp; communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🎁 <strong>What You’ll Get:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>🎓 Full training — no experience needed</li>\n  <li>💸 Uncapped earnings &amp; incentives</li>\n  <li>🚀 Fast career growth</li>\n  <li>✈️ Local &amp; overseas exposure</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>⚡ Who We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>✅ Positive, motivated &amp; eager-to-learn individuals</li>\n  <li>🎓 Fresh grads &amp; ORD personnel welcome!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>📩 Apply now &amp; kickstart your journey with us! 🌈</strong></p>",
